<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3147570" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="CHG" oldref="3">To open the <link href="text/swriter/01/05150101.xhp" name="AutoFormat for Tables">AutoFormat for Tables</link> dialog, click in a table cell, and then choose <emph>Table - AutoFormat</emph>.</paragraph>
